tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE CommunicationLogs (
    log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    agent_id INT NOT NULL,
    member_id INT NOT NULL,
    provider_id INT NOT NULL,
    interaction TEXT,
    resolution TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE communication_logs (
  log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  agent_id INT NOT NULL,
  member_id INT NOT NULL,
  provider_id INT NOT NULL,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  interaction_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE communication_logs_agents (
    communication_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    agent_id INT,
    member_id INT,
    provider_id INT,
    communication_text TEXT,
    communication_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE communication_logs_members (
    communication_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    agent_id INT,
    member_id INT,
    provider_id INT,
    communication_text TEXT,
    communication_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE communication_logs_providers (
    communication_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    agent_id INT,
    member_id INT,
    provider_id INT,
    communication_text TEXT,
    communication_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE communication_logs (
	log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	agent_id INT,
	member_id INT,
	healthcare_provider_id INT,
	communication_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
	communication_type TEXT,
	communication_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE agent_communication_logs (
	log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	agent_id INT,
	member_id INT,
	hcp_id INT,
	communication_date TIMESTAMP,
	communication_type VARCHAR(255),
	communication_content TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE agents (
	agent_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	agent_name VARCHAR(255),
	agent_role VARCHAR(255),
	agency_name VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE members (
	member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	member_name VARCHAR(255),
	email_address VARCHAR(255),
	phone_number VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE healthcare_providers (
	hcp_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	hcp_name VARCHAR(255),
	hcp_specialty VARCHAR(255),
	hcp_location VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE disputes (
	dispute_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	claim_id INT,
	member_id INT,
	agent_id INT,
	hcp_id INT,
	status VARCHAR(50)
)
